=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Guides_Tour_of_UGens_ex36 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_dark pure_tone sound, with complex oscillator character around 301 Hz, featuring punchy attack and sustained envelope, filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character, and spectrally simple.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_dark
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: simple
  spectral_flux_normalized: stable
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 301.3973
  harmonic_decay_rate: -15.9777
  harmonic_regularity: 0.5007
  pitch_clarity: 102.1166
  inharmonicity: 0.0029
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -4.2320
  resonance_freq: 301.4648

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Tour of UGens Example 36
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Guides/Tour_of_UGens.html
// Tags: Tour_of_UGens, Guides
// ---
// --- Example 36 ---
{ SinOsc.ar(300, 0, 0.2) }.play;
{ SinOsc.ar(300, 0, 0.2).abs }.play;
{ SinOsc.ar(300, 0, 0.2).max(0) }.play;
{ SinOsc.ar(300, 0).squared * 0.2 }.play;
{ SinOsc.ar(300, 0).cubed * 0.2 }.play;
